17T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf5ebf0bde122ce80086e4b7eb251a68cc32a746","tid":1659927,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"佢依家仲係咪用家居電話做訪問<br />\n如果係多數都唔係後生仔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nanyway推咗先"},{"pid":"22be4a2fa30f2403ddf43e6e6a1443ee2fee703d","tid":1659927,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c957bc195bf48d6cf01a4c6078e2b2ad00f623a","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"大家好，我地係一群熱愛香港的小市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地委托左鍾庭耀教授幫我地發起港大型民調及公投，希望多個有公信力的平台凝聚香港人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本土內部共識</span></strong>，堅決咁話比個港共政府聽，香港人一撚定要你交出真相及回應市民要求，就算再過幾多耐都好，我地一樣唔會遺忘及放棄。<br />\n<br />\n同時，透過鍾教授係國際的名望同影響力，會有一份完整而科學化的報告<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">向世界各國宣傳</span></strong>香港人的民意及呼叫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已經有好多機構做緊民調，點解我地要衝出尼柒﹖﹖﹖</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n根據我地的觀察，市場上已經有好多唔同有具公信力機構每星期都會按不同事件做民調。<br />\n<br />\n但是，由於每日都有太多慘劇/ 警暴事件，<strong>好多時做完個民調之後，大眾的焦點已經轉移</strong>。正正是這種一波未平一波又起的風氣，令到香港人就算行行下街比黑警拉左/ 非禮/ 打鑊金，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">過左1-2 日又無左件事<strong>(明明應該係核彈)</strong></span></strong>，公眾焦點又轉移左去第2粒核彈。<br />\n<br />\n於是，我們提出一份滾動調查及公投。<br />\n<br />\n所謂滾動調查是一連串在不同時段的民意調查，所問的內容都是相同，用意是了解民意的轉變，按時段的轉移，我們希望可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持續咁追蹤一些在已經發生左好耐的核彈上的意見。同時，亦會對一些近期核彈做民調。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">為什麼要持續咁追蹤一些在已經發生左好耐的核彈上的民意</span></ins></em></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n我地認為現時警察的失控源自721元朗黑幫恐怖襲擊及831太子黑警恐怖襲擊事件。<br />\n<br />\n7月21日，黑警縱容黑幫同圍打人，無視法律，至今仍未為事件作出正式而完整交代<br />\n8月31日，黑警沖入太子站，無差別攻擊市民，趕走記者，最後什至出現打死人疑雲，至今仍未為事件作出完整CCTV作交代<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">從黑警角度，正正就是以上2 件大事件都可以無人問責，佢地先會咁夠膽不停勾結黑社會，福鍵幫，地方流氓日日無差別攻擊市民而又可以消搖法外。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">試諗下，</span></span></strong>如果我地有份嚴禁而有公信力的的長期民意調，透過民意/ 國際壓力可以<strong>迫到港共要懲罰涉及這兩次恐襲的指揮官及當席黑警。黑警內部一定會好撚驚，</strong>人人自危，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>因為佢地認為最唔可能的調查/ 懲罰出現了</ins></span></strong>。為左自保一定會有人走出尼為了自保而篤灰。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家要記住，而家維持緊香港黑警集團並不是警例，紀律，義氣，而係恐懼</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n佢地而家之所以死都唔割，做錯咩都好只係交出一句「不完美可接受有改善空間」就當解左話。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢地知道同恐懼，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一旦有黑警出事/ 被法律制裁到，一撚定會有人出來為自保而篤灰</span></strong></span></strong></span>，到時個個都死。<br />\n<br />\n政府日日都叫我地割，因為佢知道割蓆，可以好撚大威力。<br />\n<br />\n在勇武派街頭抗爭成本愈來愈大的情況下，我地一於要民意及國際壓力，迫到迫到黑警一定要搵人祭旗。所以，<strong>李漢民，遊乃強你班仆街聽住，你地係政府的立場只是condom，用完就即棄。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>當我地一方民意同影響力強大到迫政府棄condom，一定會有狗出尼篤灰隊死你地班仆街。</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><br />\n所以，黑警入面一有一個人割蓆/篤灰，我地就可以打散黑集團。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位連登仔你地聽撚住，而家你見到這個POST 果陣，鍾庭耀教授開緊記招公布緊<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>民調/ 公投以及眾籌大計。</ins></span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></strong>當大家收到PORI 香港民意研究所打尼的電話，停一停 諗一諗，唔好屌柒打尼果個人住，禮貌D，用心去做民調。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為你用心的回答，我地先可以有個最強大最巨民意的調查報告，迫到港共跪底係到瀨西。</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n除左會以721 及831 做滾動調查，我們都會加插不同問題上市民的意見及推動公投<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當眾籌大計細節出爐</span>，我地希望<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">月入50K的連登仔可以大大力用錢支援我地</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">同時，鍾庭耀教授希望大家可以幫手訂閱佢個channel (目標2000人，愈多愈好)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>勇武，你可能唔夠膽上到前線<br />\n遊行，你可能唔得閑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但屌你，禁個制訂閱個channel 同課金眾籌，咁簡單得啦掛!!!!!!</span></ins></span> <br />\n</span></strong><br />\nLINK：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw%2Ffeatured&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=f2f574c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw/featured</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkcQqBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkcQqBJ.jpg&h=66793dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，寧化飛灰，不作浮塵<br />\n我勢弱言輕，決不虛作無聲</span></span></ins></em></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"一定要有實體票站<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 點樣課金?"},{"pid":"572ae175ca56e905b0a0ffac57b6aeeb012fff1e","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"我地努力做，一建立到眾籌平台就再公布<br />\n而家大家可以訂閱左個youtube頻道支持下先"},{"pid":"21a4098c6e592de10bfc085b8c593be32be9b951","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5ebf0bde122ce80086e4b7eb251a68cc32a746","tid":1659927,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"佢依家仲係咪用家居電話做訪問<br />\n如果係多數都唔係後生仔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nanyway推咗先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"按鐘教授計劃我地係隨機抽樣"},{"pid":"9538b1cc09f5cb0c432ef80ecb81dd77314f3851","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T22:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fc1c1c4959be2493aa173a37bc00b82a494342d","tid":1659927,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T22:53:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bc75cc0c540c3889e063e81bd33c38e5815fcc5","tid":1659927,"uid":190396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a764f0d5f56acba670c5bdd77df18e84f9043b2","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:36:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81c28f36ea1a2e4e549300d2bebfdb57561689a5","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:44:13.000Z","msg":"有acoount幫手推"},{"pid":"15585e30e7931df77e540f0238c0dc5674812944","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:54:57.000Z","msg":"屌你，連登仔去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb2d740d80f66f3d815058a830919af91b2adeb","tid":1659927,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:29:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}